Class Time

  • java.lang.Object
    • classesObjects.example1.Time

  • public class Time
extends java.lang.Object
    the class stores time in a 24-hour format. hour = 9, minute = 20 represents the time 9:20 am hour = 17, minute = 35 represents the time 5:35 pm
